        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Would the Chancellor of the Exchequer explain why making a central hole in a threepenny bit would throw a heavy burden on those in charge? It is a common form of coin on the Continent and would fulfill the purpose we all have in mind.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
